63	     * Whether this action modifies a record (has a before/after hash).
64	     *
65	     * All actions listed here are subject to the schema-level CHECK constraints
66	     * (chk_modification_requires_after_hash, chk_transition_requires_before_hash)
67	     * and the application-layer guard in EloquentAuditEventRepository::record().
